{"tid":397142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知道羅興亞民族呢一點, 你會認同緬甸政府大清洗行動","createTime":"2017-09-12T09:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T04:25:38.000Z","uid":82646,"like":148,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c48049040956b5557115c5e0eb4574f4aa005548","tid":397142,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"羅興亞人（Rohingya people），緬甸若開邦阿拉干地區一族，主要居於近孟加拉邊界的貌奪和布帝洞鎮，信奉<strong>伊斯蘭教</strong>，膚色黝黑，臉相、語言系屬、宗教接近孟加拉人，故羅興亞人在緬甸被視為孟加拉<strong>偷渡者。</strong><br />\n<br />\n在緬甸燒殺擄掠，燒毀上百個村莊，<span style=\"color: red;\">屠殺超過評十萬名佛教徒平民</span>的英軍孟加拉V支隊，大多是羅興亞人的祖先。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瘋狂繁殖時期</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1911年</span>，緬甸西部的羅興亞穆斯林人口從<span style=\"color: red;\">5.9萬</span>增加到了<span style=\"color: red;\">17.9萬。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2013年</span>，約有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">130萬羅興亞人</span></span>生活在緬甸境內<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單而言:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">羅興亞民族 ～  香港南亞裔 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n認同   正皮<br />\n不認同 負皮"},{"pid":"fe71383516be880c3f2afad1777de3a237495e21","tid":397142,"uid":130394,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"唔幫佢絕對係冇錯, 歐美國家示威嗰班垃圾又畀佢哋入嚟囉. 到時啲難民又周圍搞事唔好問點解. 人道撚永遠係最嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88eda6977a17724494298abfb77850e3ff79c936","tid":397142,"uid":28624,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"種族清洗劣等民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包容 包你老母咩<br />\n醜陋既物種就應該消失啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba3edaca259c0fb2e69db9af6b944186a2fe2f0","tid":397142,"uid":118120,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羅興亞人（Rohingya people），緬甸若開邦阿拉干地區一族，主要居於近孟加拉邊界的貌奪和布帝洞鎮，信奉<strong>伊斯蘭教</strong>，膚色黝黑，臉相、語言系屬、宗教接近孟加拉人，故羅興亞人在緬甸被視為孟加拉<strong>偷渡者。</strong><br />\n<br />\n在緬甸燒殺擄掠，燒毀上百個村莊，<span style=\"color: red;\">屠殺超過評十萬名佛教徒平民</span>的英軍孟加拉V支隊，大多是羅興亞人的祖先。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瘋狂繁殖時期</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1911年</span>，緬甸西部的羅興亞穆斯林人口從<span style=\"color: red;\">5.9萬</span>增加到了<span style=\"color: red;\">17.9萬。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2013年</span>，約有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">130萬羅興亞人</span></span>生活在緬甸境內<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單而言:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">羅興亞民族 ～  香港南亞裔 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n認同   正皮<br />\n不認同 負皮</blockquote><br />\n係仲衰過香港南亞人<br />\n<br />\n羅興亞人係想殺曬本地人佔地立國 <br />\n<br />\n聯合國同情羅興亞人 根本係支持佢地侵略緬甸"},{"pid":"76e4f5110f82a97d5c4b41d3fbac628fdd752c57","tid":397142,"uid":73281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"就好似班蝗想係香港立國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e7afe16a7da5fa01c471a4f9c39d50cbd9928d","tid":397142,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"求情個d大部份係回教伊斯蘭<br />\n<br />\n大家都係恐怖主義"},{"pid":"7f8c12f5df2409ddf934ff5adf45c85f7e48b6c0","tid":397142,"uid":44925,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:09:26.000Z","msg":"啲左膠成日屌鳩昂山素姬真係on 柒鳩<br />\n佢代表既係緬甸人<br />\n唔係代表你左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10ea211cd9eced0574f1d1539e51958786929b9","tid":397142,"uid":24345,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"唔殺到時好似阿富汗咁由佛教國家變伊斯蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a222c7b00e8da70c6765a8a2be667c7017392ce